name: Juice WRLD modded
description:
So I just made this mod with my friend domidev (check his itch.io). 

It's basicaly fnf, but with Juice WRLD songs. We are currently working on adding Juice's character and making more songs. 

I would appreciate if you give us feedback so we can improve the mod.

Do not hesitate to tell us what song you want in the comment!

 If you get any issue please report them to me!

 Enjoy!
